#feature-section-right
  .description
    %h2 Manage all your jobs with ease
    %p No more guessing which job still needs to filled. Talentwiz allows you to track all your job postings with ease. Our dashboard effectively displays all your jobs in a central location.
    %ul 
      %li 
        %span Visual pipeline of where the hiring process stands
      %li 
        %span Customize your recruitment process for each job
      %li 
        %span Filter jobs by status, location, name and type

  .image
    %img(src="/tmp/homepage-dashboard2.png")

#feature-section-left
  .description
    %h2 Accept & Manage Applications Online
    %p Don't let applications fill up your e-mail. Talentwiz allows you to accept all applications online directly through your branded career portal.  
    %ul 
      %li
        %span Build a great career portal to promote job opportunities
      %li
        %span Customized application form 
      %li
        %span Easily rank and filter applicants
      %li 
        %span Mass actions for candidates
  .image
    %img(src="/tmp/build-talent-pool.png")

#feature-section-right
  .description
    %h2 Centralized Candidate Management
    %p Losing track of a candidate and their standing in your hiring process can be costly. Talentwiz allows you track all the information about a candidate in a central location. 
    %ul 
      %li 
        %span  All contact information & CV
      %li 
        %span Collaborate with teammates 
      %li 
        %span Track all communication with an applicant
      %li 
        %span Centralized assessments and evaluations

  .image
    %img(src="/tmp/applicant-profile-screenshot.png")


